---
title: Database Migration Flow
description: Complete database migration workflow using Drizzle ORM
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% Development Phase
    Start([🎯 Start Schema Change])
    EditSchema[✏️ Edit Schema File<br/>packages/db/src/schemas/]
    GenerateMigration[🔧 Generate Migration<br/>pnpm db:generate]
    ReviewSQL[👁️ Review SQL File<br/>drizzle/migrations/]

    %% Decision Points
    SafeSQL{🤔 SQL Safe?}
    EditSQL[✏️ Edit Migration<br/>Manually]

    %% Local Testing
    TestLocal[🧪 Test Locally<br/>pnpm db:migrate]
    CheckStudio[🔍 Verify in Drizzle Studio<br/>pnpm db:studio]
    LocalWorks{✅ Works<br/>Correctly?}

    %% Rollback Path
    Rollback[↩️ Rollback Migration<br/>pnpm db:drop]
    FixSchema[🔧 Fix Schema]

    %% Version Control
    CommitFiles[💾 Commit Files<br/>- schema.ts<br/>- migration.sql<br/>- meta.json]
    PushGitHub[⬆️ Push to GitHub]

    %% CI/CD Phase
    GitHubActions[⚙️ GitHub Actions<br/>CI Pipeline]
    RunTests[🧪 Run Tests]
    CIPasses{✅ CI Passes?}
    FixTests[🔧 Fix Tests]

    %% Deployment Phase
    DeployVercel[🚀 Deploy to Vercel]
    RunMigration[🔄 Run Migration<br/>on Neon DB]
    MigrationSuccess{✅ Migration<br/>Success?}

    %% Production Verification
    CheckLogs[📝 Check Vercel Logs]
    VerifyProd[✅ Verify Production]
    MonitorErrors[📊 Monitor Errors]

    %% Failure Path
    MigrationFails[❌ Migration Failed]
    Emergency[🚨 Emergency Rollback]
    RestoreBackup[💾 Restore DB Backup]
    Investigate[🔍 Investigate Issue]

    %% Success Path
    Success([✨ Migration Complete])
    UpdateDocs[📄 Update Documentation]

    %% Flow
    Start --> EditSchema
    EditSchema --> GenerateMigration
    GenerateMigration --> ReviewSQL
    ReviewSQL --> SafeSQL

    SafeSQL -->|No ✗| EditSQL
    EditSQL --> ReviewSQL
    SafeSQL -->|Yes ✓| TestLocal

    TestLocal --> CheckStudio
    CheckStudio --> LocalWorks

    LocalWorks -->|No ✗| Rollback
    Rollback --> FixSchema
    FixSchema --> EditSchema
    LocalWorks -->|Yes ✓| CommitFiles

    CommitFiles --> PushGitHub
    PushGitHub --> GitHubActions
    GitHubActions --> RunTests
    RunTests --> CIPasses

    CIPasses -->|No ✗| FixTests
    FixTests --> EditSchema
    CIPasses -->|Yes ✓| DeployVercel

    DeployVercel --> RunMigration
    RunMigration --> MigrationSuccess

    MigrationSuccess -->|No ✗| MigrationFails
    MigrationFails --> Emergency
    Emergency --> RestoreBackup
    RestoreBackup --> Investigate
    Investigate --> FixSchema

    MigrationSuccess -->|Yes ✓| CheckLogs
    CheckLogs --> VerifyProd
    VerifyProd --> MonitorErrors
    MonitorErrors --> Success
    Success --> UpdateDocs

    %% Migration Types
    subgraph MigrationTypes[Migration Types]
        AddTable[➕ Add Table]
        AddColumn[➕ Add Column]
        AlterColumn[🔄 Alter Column]
        DropColumn[➖ Drop Column]
        AddIndex[📊 Add Index]
        AddConstraint[🔒 Add Constraint]
    end

    %% Safety Checks
    subgraph SafetyChecks[Safety Checks]
        NoDataLoss[✅ No Data Loss]
        Reversible[↩️ Reversible]
        BackwardCompat[🔄 Backward Compatible]
        Performance[⚡ Performance Impact]
    end

    ReviewSQL -.->|Check| SafetyChecks
    SafeSQL -.->|Review| MigrationTypes

    %% Styling
    classDef development fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef testing fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef cicd fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef deployment fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef failure fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#06b6d4,stroke:#0891b2,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#6b7280,stroke:#4b5563,color:#fff

    class EditSchema,GenerateMigration,ReviewSQL,EditSQL development
    class TestLocal,CheckStudio,LocalWorks,Rollback,FixSchema testing
    class CommitFiles,PushGitHub,GitHubActions,RunTests,CIPasses,FixTests cicd
    class DeployVercel,RunMigration,MigrationSuccess,CheckLogs,VerifyProd deployment
    class MigrationFails,Emergency,RestoreBackup,Investigate failure
    class Success,UpdateDocs,MonitorErrors success
    class SafeSQL,LocalWorks,CIPasses,MigrationSuccess decision
```
